    <string name="perm_dialog_title">Network &amp; Privacy</string>
    <string name="perm_dialog_msg">KlippShell requires network access to establish a direct interface with your printer\'s Moonraker API, as well as notification permissions to send you critical alerts and print milestones (e.g., print complete or errors) while you are watching TV or using other apps. An internet connection is required for OTA update checks, the provision of status assets for the Android TV Launcher, as well as for advanced companion features. Data security is our top priority: communication takes place exclusively locally between your device and the printer. No control or telemetry data is transmitted to external servers.</string>
